    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(…) Domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab eius nativitate
                        millesimo centesimo nonagesimo septimo, quinto kal. (…). Manifestus sum ego
                                <persName><name ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildebrandinus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Rainerius">Rainerii</name></persName> quia (…)
                        vendo et trado tibi <persName><name ref="Widoctus"
                            >Guidotto</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Passavanti"
                                >Passavanti</name></persName> tres meas videlicet (…). Prima est
                        campus in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/691">Carraie</placeName>
                        et est tres quarre (…), caput in via publica et aliquantulum in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Cecius">Ceci</name></persName>, aliud caput in
                        terra et media fossa (…), in terra et media fossa <persName><name
                                ref="Vivianus">Viviani</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Amicus">Amichi</name></persName> et aliquantulum in via
                        publica. (…) quondam <persName><name ref="Brunicardus"
                            >Brunicardi</name></persName> et in terra et media fossa <persName><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Raginerii</name></persName> et Misolo(…). (…)ampus
                        cum arboribus (…) ibidem ubi dicitur Campovinceri et est (…). Que tenet unum
                        caput in via publica, aliud caput in terra et media fossa (…), (…)quantulu
                        in terra et media fossa <persName><name ref="Hubaldus"
                            >Ubaldi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Cassese"
                                >Cassesi</name></persName>, amboque latera in terra et media fossa
                        (…) quam detinet <persName><name ref="Terrescus">Terresci</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Deotisalvi">Detisalvi</name></persName>. Tertia
                        petia de terra est ortalis cum arboribus ibidem (…), caput in via publica,
                        aliud caput in terra et media fossa Ubaldi quondam Cassesi et filiorum
                        quondam (…), latus unum tenet in terra Amichi et nepotum, aliud in terra et
                        media fossa quam michi reservo (…) que est per mensura tres quarre vel si
                        plus est. (…) Quas tres petias de terris detinent <persName><name
                                ref="Stephanus">Stephanus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Centone">Centoni</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Fanus">Fanis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Stephanellus">Stephanelli</name></persName> per tenimentum,
                        unde reddunt in singulo anno de suprascripta prima petia de terra staria
                        decem et octo blave scilicet novem de grano et novem de milio. Et de
                        predicta secunda petia de terra staria decem et octo blave scilicet staria
                        novem de grano et novem staria de milio. De iamdicta tertia petia de terra
                        staria duodecim blave, scilicet sex staria grani et sex de milio. (…)
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandinus"
                            >Ildebrandini</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Marranus"
                                >Marani</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido"
                                >Guidonis</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Azo"
                                >Atthi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Richardus">Riccardi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Palarminus">Palarmini</name></persName> rogatorum <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"
                                ><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni
                        Frederici imperatoris post traditam complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
